getFeedIds

java.util.List<java.lang.String> getFeedIds()
Get the stored IDs of all the feeds in here. Used to keep this in sync with the DB. In some cases things can get put in here without being put in the DB (for instance, OutOfMemoryError or hardware failure during feed parsing).
